  "content": "<p data-pid=\"mcmgRJk4\">。。。Anki，作为一个学习APP，不只是个背单词的，还能背生物、化学、语文、物理、数学。。。等等，只针对英语的话，也有很多用途。</p><p data-pid=\"MOzLN8le\">比如，写作文，想到一个比较low的词，怎样反应出一个高级一点的词呢？</p><p data-pid=\"5HQhEk-k\">可以这样用 Anki 来记：</p><figure data-size=\"small\"><noscript><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-cf78e405763315cc2e5087d182bd04f1_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"small\" data-rawwidth=\"720\" data-rawheight=\"1280\" data-original-token=\"v2-41049e3069e82c25b85dd963e25122c6\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-27dbbd23841ac5cd5139a857054cebf8_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"720\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-cf78e405763315cc2e5087d182bd04f1_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;720&#39; height=&#39;1280&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"small\" data-rawwidth=\"720\" data-rawheight=\"1280\" data-original-token=\"v2-41049e3069e82c25b85dd963e25122c6\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-27dbbd23841ac5cd5139a857054cebf8_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"720\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-cf78e405763315cc2e5087d182bd04f1_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-cf78e405763315cc2e5087d182bd04f1_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><p data-pid=\"XQ249lif\"><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/34891600\" class=\"internal\" target=\"_blank\">简单「Anki」英语作文词汇实战</a> </p><p data-pid=\"3I91IpGm\">还有些熟词生义，平时背单词根本背不到，只能做题积累，那么用 Anki 来背也很方便：</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-e70dd69de66cb4f889d9c17c8c033f64_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"720\" data-rawheight=\"559\" data-original-token=\"v2-189241f74f0e6bf17354eada2cef8f71\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-83c29cec0172f5acf685eb8ad913bf02_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"720\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-e70dd69de66cb4f889d9c17c8c033f64_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;720&#39; height=&#39;559&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"720\" data-rawheight=\"559\" data-original-token=\"v2-189241f74f0e6bf17354eada2cef8f71\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-83c29cec0172f5acf685eb8ad913bf02_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"720\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-e70dd69de66cb4f889d9c17c8c033f64_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-e70dd69de66cb4f889d9c17c8c033f64_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><p data-pid=\"rnfMyF9y\"><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/36475725\" class=\"internal\" target=\"_blank\">简单「Anki」英语熟词生义实战</a> </p><p data-pid=\"sYGV2zYs\">还有一些词性转换，背单词不一定能覆盖到，也能用 Anki：</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-1e4b9ac77c66a8eb5f6d79bd8b185541_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"720\" data-rawheight=\"440\" data-original-token=\"v2-d71384f7cc4a41a82c2b82f4b724de77\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-8d241100ecbf4d9fb965cc215263dcaf_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"720\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-1e4b9ac77c66a8eb5f6d79bd8b185541_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;720&#39; height=&#39;440&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"720\" data-rawheight=\"440\" data-original-token=\"v2-d71384f7cc4a41a82c2b82f4b724de77\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-8d241100ecbf4d9fb965cc215263dcaf_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"720\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-1e4b9ac77c66a8eb5f6d79bd8b185541_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-1e4b9ac77c66a8eb5f6d79bd8b185541_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><p data-pid=\"qBe6xdNh\"><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/36788200\" class=\"internal\" target=\"_blank\">简单「Anki」英语词性转换实战</a> </p><p data-pid=\"iq3KnSri\">总之 Anki 的用途很多，就看你的想法是怎么样的。</p>",
